headline: Disney Dining Return and Gamer Tie-Ins Could Be A Game Changer For Starbucks (SBUX)
summary: In early January 2026, Starbucks was reinstated into Disney’s 2026 Disney Dining Plan and expanded brand partnerships, including a Newegg bundle offering Starbucks gift cards with high-end RAM purchases, alongside new winter beverages and merchandise launches. This combination of renewed exposure at Disney parks and targeted cross-promotions with online and gaming-focused audiences highlights how Starbucks is working to deepen customer engagement across both physical and digital...
